rdfgears.rgl.workflow
Class Workflow

java.lang.Object
  rdfgears.rgl.workflow.function.RGLFunction
      rdfgears.rgl.workflow.Workflow

public class Workflow
extends RGLFunction

A Workflow contains a network of Processors. As the processors reference eachother, we only need to keep track of the inputs and outputs. Note: A new Workflow object with a new processor network needs to be instantiated for every processor that uses the workflow as it's function definition.

Author:
Eric Feliksik

getOutputType

public RGLType getOutputType(TypeRow inputTypes)
                      throws TypingException
Description copied from class: RGLFunction
The typechecking mechanism for this function. given a row over types, return the output type. If the processor is not defined for the input row, it must throw a TypingException. This function should never return null.

Specified by:
getOutputType in class RGLFunction
Parameters:
